{"tid":801305,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港小學正式比蝗蟲淪陷","createTime":"2018-08-31T13:48:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T14:11:20.000Z","uid":172607,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fca31df5aeca578c79d989d155e13f7a47b752f9","tid":801305,"uid":172607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T13:48:47.000Z","msg":"小五女生夢想成首富、住大屋：爸爸唔駛做廳長、周圍玩<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/214748_c0834e57cfc8ab3e24f1cd8c19ffa688.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F214748_c0834e57cfc8ab3e24f1cd8c19ffa688.png&h=6d97970c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港的土地及房屋問題近年備受關注，殊不知，土地問題亦影響到小朋友的夢想。就讀中華基督教會全完第二小學、即將升讀小六的11歲女生陳曉君，早前參加正向訓練營時，寫下4大夢想，包括：「<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">做教育部部長</span></span>（教育局局長），消除功課！做十大多錢首富！入香港中文大學！學多種外語！」<br />\n<br />\n「錢唔係萬能，但想要大屋，可以周圍跑」<br />\n<br />\n細問下始知，她想成為「十大多錢首豪」與房屋問題有關：「<span style=\"color: red;\">聽人哋講，錢唔係萬能，但我想要好大嘅屋企，可以周圍跑，周圍玩，爸爸唔洗再做廳長。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n那為何要做教育局局長？曉君指，升小五後有感功課量明顯增加，每晚做功課至7、8點，儘管仍有時間可看卡通片，卻感覺自由時間不多：「功課好多，無時間做自己想做嘅嘢！（想做咩？）睇冒險小說！」<br />\n<br />\n大陸人先會叫教育部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蝗蟲父母教出黎嘅細路就係咩都講錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁細個就咁嘅思想 第日大個唔知會變成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99c40328f36d5b15db1238c314cf86aae57177a8","tid":801305,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T13:49:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"484d2c48ae9a6abae8fb7b73a0c1c56106832417","tid":801305,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T13:58:54.000Z","msg":"大左夢想咪又係買層樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"458fa95ace019ede94635508bbde1557af7c591f","tid":801305,"uid":7632,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:00:16.000Z","msg":"起碼呢隻識尊重正（繁）體字"},{"pid":"41ae87db213587e0ae07971b6e2df90bea2bc362","tid":801305,"uid":172607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"458fa95ace019ede94635508bbde1557af7c591f","tid":801305,"uid":7632,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:00:16.000Z","msg":"起碼呢隻識尊重正（繁）體字"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:10:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ff30a926ee12b38c16a1a34c83e535e2d8f1b79","tid":801305,"uid":172607,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:11:20.000Z","msg":"香港學生已經唔係真香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}